    And a news item "HasNewsOrg TestNews" referencing "HasNewsOrg"
    And I request "/api/v1/news"
    Then the response is success
    And the response body contains JSON:
      """
      [
        {"title": "HasNewsOrg TestNews"}
      ]
      """

